Content of subdirectories:
 - common
   Anything that is common to two or ore type of server
 - battle
   Everything related only to the battles
 - chat
   Everything related to the chat
 - controller
   Everything related to the control on the client (forward to the battle, auth, etc.)
 - info
   Server giving access to REST services to access read-only information about players,
   characters and other infos. Also used to search through players and characters.
